Text: BiWeekly Sample Run Pigging Reportpig that was run to PGE on Monday came in dry with no liquids As you will notice there are a few new sample points with liquids that were accumilated Please see attached documents

Needles PGE Weekly Reportplease see last weeks sample run results This weeks sample run will not take place on Thursday due to PGEs request and will be performed on Friday the th instead Should still receive the results prior to next weeks report Started decontamination and filter change outs of the inlet filter seperator at the Solexol Plant both filter seperators on the discharge of the Solexol Plant the filter seperator at Transwesterns PGE measurement station Operations and contractors are gearing up today Thursday to start the decontamination on the inlet filter at the Solexol plant which will set the pace for the remaining seperators Operations has been informed that PGE will be performing a decontamination and filter change out at their filter seperator on the inlet of the PGE Topac compressor station This has been scheduled for April th
PGE Monthly Sample Resultssample results are looking better See attached for this months sample resultsThanksRandy
